y', 'surface': 'by', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 314565, 'end_time': 314705}, {'text': 'then', 'surface': 'then,', 'punctuation': ',', 'begin_time': 314705, 'end_time': 314925}, {'text': 'Mitch', 'surface': 'Mitch', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 315045, 'end_time': 315165}, {'text': 'had', 'surface': 'had', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 315165, 'end_time': 315245}, {'text': 'brought', 'surface': 'brought', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 315245, 'end_time': 315465}, {'text': 'Cam', 'surface': 'Cam', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 315465, 'end_time': 315785}, {'text': 'home', 'surface': 'home,', 'punctuation': ',', 'begin_time': 315785, 'end_time': 316045}, {'text': 'so', 'surface': 'so', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 316085, 'end_time': 316245}, {'text': 'I', 'surface': 'I', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 316245, 'end_time': 316265}, {'text': 'was', 'surface': 'was', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 316265, 'end_time': 316425}, {'text': 'golden', 'surface': 'golden.', 'punctuation': '.', 'begin_time': 316425, 'end_time': 316865}, {'text': 'Claire', 'surface': 'Claire', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 318225, 'end_time': 318625}, {'text': 'just', 'surface': 'just', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 318625, 'end_time': 318805}, {'text': 'needs', 'surface': 'needs', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 318805, 'end_time': 318985}, {'text': 'a', 'surface': 'a', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 318985, 'end_time': 319105}, {'text': 'little', 'surface': 'little', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 319105, 'end_time': 319205}, {'text': 'time', 'surface': 'time.', 'punctuation': '.', 'begin_time': 319205, 'end_time': 319905}, {'text': 'Then', 'surface': 'Then', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 321485, 'end_time': 321905}, {'text': 'trust', 'surface': 'trust', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 321905, 'end_time': 322325}, {'text': 'me', 'surface': 'me,', 'punctuation': ',', 'begin_time': 322325, 'end_time': 322525}, {'text': "she'll", 'surface': "she'll", 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 322685, 'end_time': 322745}, {'text': 'be', 'surface': 'be', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 322745, 'end_time': 322845}, {'text': 'the', 'surface': 'the', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 322845, 'end_time': 322985}, {'text': 'most', 'surface': 'most', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 322985, 'end_time': 323125}, {'text': 'loyal', 'surface': 'loyal', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 323125, 'end_time': 323505}, {'text': 'friend', 'surface': 'friend', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 323505, 'end_time': 323745}, {'text': "you've", 'surface': "you've", 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 323745, 'end_time': 323965}, {'text': 'ever', 'surface': 'ever', 'punctuation': '', 'begin_time': 323965, 'end_time': 324105}, {'text': 'had', 'surface': 'had.', 'punctuation': '.', 'begin_time': 324105, 'end_time': 324385}], 'sentences': [{'sentence_id': 0, 'begin_time': 50, 'end_time': 1130, 'text': 'Okay, the truth?'}, {'sentence_id': 1, 'begin_time': 2010, 'end_time': 3990, 'text': "I sometimes feel like you don't like me."}, {'sentence_id': 2, 'begin_time': 6130, 'end_time': 7790, 'text': 'Powerful, powerful stuff.'}, {'sentence_id': 3, 'begin_time': 8690, 'end_time': 10650, 'text': 'Claire, tell us how that makes you feel.'}, {'sentence_id': 4, 'begin_time': 10910, 'end_time': 12190, 'text': "Right now I'm feeling a lot of anger."}, {'sentence_id': 5, 'begin_time': 12310, 'end_time': 13790, 'text': "No, no, don't tell me, tell her."}, {'sentence_id': 6, 'begin_time': 14530, 'end_time': 16230, 'text': "Gloria, right now I'm really angry at Phil."}, {'sentence_id': 7, 'begin_time': 16350, 'end_time': 17870, 'text': "Oh, let's respect the process."}, {'sentence_id': 8, 'begin_time': 20600, 'end_time': 23360, 'text': "Gloria, I don't know why you think I don't like you."}, {'sentence_id': 9, 'begin_time': 23540, 'end_time': 25940, 'text': 'Well, sometimes when you see me, you make that face.'}, {'sentence_id': 10, 'begin_time': 26040, 'end_time': 26540, 'text': 'What face?'}, {'sentence_id': 11, 'begin_time': 26860, 'end_time': 27240, 'text': 'Like this?'}, {'sentence_id': 12, 'begin_time': 28040, 'end_time': 28760, 'text': 'I do not make a face like that.'}, {'sentence_id': 13, 'begin_time': 28760, 'end_time': 29520, 'text': 'Oh my God.'}, {'sentence_id': 14, 'begin_time': 29780, 'end_time': 30680, 'text': 'That is so clear.'}, {'sentence_id': 15, 'begin_time': 30740, 'end_time': 31020, 'text': 'Mitchell.'}, {'sentence_id': 16, 'begin_time': 31440, 'end_time': 31660, 'text': 'See?'}, {'sentence_id': 17, 'begin_time': 32240, 'end_time': 33540, 'text': 'She does that with everyone.'}, {'sentence_id': 18, 'begin_time': 34460, 'end_time': 35100, 'text': "It's just her face."}, {'sentence_id': 19, 'begin_time': 35100, 'end_time': 37040, 'text': "No, it's not just the face."}, {'sentence_id': 20, 'begin_time': 37700, 'end_time': 41000, 'text': 'From the beginning, I feel like Manny and I are not welcome in this family.'}, {'sentence_id': 21, 'begin_time': 41180, 'end_time': 42420, 'text': 'That is so crazy.'}, {'sentence_id': 22, 'begin_time': 42660, 'end_time': 43940, 'text': "No, it's not so crazy."}, {'sentence_id': 23, 'begin_time': 43940, 'end_time': 45060, 'text': "It's how I feel."}, {'sentence_id': 24, 'begin_time': 49270, 'end_time': 51610, 'text': 'I am sorry, if you feel that way.'}, {'sentence_id': 25, 'begin_time': 51850, 'end_time': 52490, 'text': 'I really am.'}, {'sentence_id': 26, 'begin_time': 52930, 'end_time': 57890, 'text': 'Because from the moment I met you, I have tried to make you feel comfortable with us.'}, {'sentence_id': 27, 'begin_time': 59250, 'end_time': 60730, 'text': "You think it's only in my head?"}, {'sentence_id': 28, 'begin_time': 60990, 'end_time': 62870, 'text': "No, kind, I don't know."}, {'sentence_id': 29, 'begin_time': 62870, 'end_time': 66710, 'text': 'I mean, we really love having you and Manny and our family.'}, {'sentence_id': 30, 'begin_time': 66890, 'end_time': 67270, 'text': 'Really?'}, {'sentence_id': 31, 'begin_time': 68470, 'end_time': 70610, 'text': "So, you don't have to be so defensive."}, {'sentence_id': 32, 'begin_time': 71790, 'end_time': 72970, 'text': "I do that, don't I?"}, {'sentence_id': 33, 'begin_time': 75490, 'end_time': 77010, 'text': "I'm feeling a hug."}, {'sentence_id': 34, 'begin_time': 78950, 'end_time': 81870, 'text': 'I was thinking group hug, but this is nice.'}, {'sentence_id': 35, 'begin_time': 81870, 'end_time': 84310, 'text': "I'd be there if I could, oh my god, there's hugging."}, {'sentence_id': 36, 'begin_time': 84970, 'end_time': 86310, 'text': 'Haley, get off the phone already.'}, {'sentence_id': 37, 'begin_time': 86310, 'end_time': 87290, 'text': 'Where did you go?'}, {'sentence_id': 38, 'begin_time': 87970, 'end_time': 88890, 'text': 'You heard him?'}, {'sentence_id': 39, 'begin_time': 88910, 'end_time': 89870, 'text': 'You said get out of here.'}, {'sentence_id': 40, 'begin_time': 89950, 'end_time': 91670, 'text': "Oh my god, you're such a girl."}, {'sentence_id': 41, 'begin_time': 91750, 'end_time': 94210, 'text': 'Dad, look, I was coming to get a beer anyways.'}, {'sentence_id': 42, 'begin_time': 94950, 'end_time': 95530, 'text': 'Nice apology.'}, {'sentence_id': 43, 'begin_time': 95730, 'end_time': 96490, 'text': 'Nice beer.'}, {'sentence_id': 44, 'begin_time': 97970, 'end_time': 100250, 'text': "Hey, there's our little roust about."}, {'sentence_id': 45, 'begin_time': 100690, 'end_time': 102810, 'text': 'You look like you patched things up pretty good, huh?'}, {'sentence_id': 46, 'begin_time': 102810, 'end_time': 103210, 'text': 'Yeah.'}, {'sentence_id': 47, 'begin_time': 104390, 'end_time': 106470, 'text': 'We can learn so much from the children.'}, {'sentence_id': 48, 'begin_time': 107030, 'end_time': 108810, 'text': ', but it seems kind of silly now,'}, {'sentence_id': 49, 'begin_time': 108810, 'end_time': 115930, 'text': "which we've been fighting for lunch for lunch every day,"}, {'sentence_id': 50, 'begin_time': 116870, 'end_time': 119830, 'text': 'I made fun of him because his mom used to dig coal.'}, {'sentence_id': 51, 'begin_time': 121230, 'end_time': 121410, 'text': 'What?'}, {'sentence_id': 52, 'begin_time': 121950, 'end_time': 123770, 'text': 'He said you were a cold digger.'}, {'sentence_id': 53, 'begin_time': 123870, 'end_time': 125610, 'text': 'Okay, I think we can move on.'}, {'sentence_id': 54, 'begin_time': 126190, 'end_time': 127630, 'text': 'Who said I was a cold digger?'}, {'sentence_id': 55, 'begin_time': 127950, 'end_time': 129290, 'text': "That's what my mom told me."}, {'sentence_id': 56, 'begin_time': 129630, 'end_time': 130470, 'text': "What's a cold digger?"}, {'sentence_id': 57, 'begin_time': 130470, 'end_time': 130870, 'text': "What's a cold digger?"}, {'sentence_id': 58, 'begin_time': 131130, 'end_time': 132050, 'text': 'Sweetheart, you heard it wrong.'}, {'sentence_id': 59, 'begin_time': 132050, 'end_time': 132850, 'text': "It's gold digger."}, {'sentence_id': 60, 'begin_time': 132990, 'end_time': 134370, 'text': "I'm going to have to call you back."}, {'sentence_id': 61, 'begin_time': 134610, 'end_time': 138050, 'text': 'Well, I really do not think that I remember ever saying that.'}, {'sentence_id': 62, 'begin_time': 138230, 'end_time': 139950, 'text': 'Well, you sent in the car.'}, {'sentence_id': 63, 'begin_time': 140470, 'end_time': 141510, 'text': 'You said at Christmas.'}, {'sentence_id': 64, 'begin_time': 141910, 'end_time': 143270, 'text': 'You sent Mexican rock out.'}, {'sentence_id': 65, 'begin_time': 143270, 'end_time': 146030, 'text': 'Hey, Mr. leaves the sweatshirts at school every day'}, {'sentence_id': 66, 'begin_time': 146030, 'end_time': 146830, 'text': 'and suddenly remembers everything.'}, {'sentence_id': 67, 'begin_time': 147130, 'end_time': 147310, 'text': 'Thank you.'}, {'sentence_id': 68, 'begin_time': 148690, 'end_time': 150870, 'text': 'And it was all in my head, huh?'}, {'sentence_id': 69, 'begin_time': 150890, 'end_time': 156110, 'text': 'Oh, listen, Gloria, it was like a year ago before I knew you...'}, {'sentence_id': 70, 'begin_time': 156110, 'end_time': 158870, 'text': 'Nice going. Not my mom and my sister are fighting.'}, {'sentence_id': 71, 'begin_time': 163730, 'end_time': 165990, 'text': 'If I say something that everybody else is thinking,'}, {'sentence_id': 72, 'begin_time': 166090, 'end_time': 167450, 'text': 'does that make me a mean person?'}, {'sentence_id': 73, 'begin_time': 167850, 'end_time': 175530, 'text': 'Or does it make me a brave person, one who was courageous enough to stand up and say something'}, {'sentence_id': 74, 'begin_time': 175530, 'end_time': 178950, 'text': "behind someone's back to 10-year-old?"}, {'sentence_id': 75, 'begin_time': 181380, 'end_time': 182760, 'text': "Well, she's pissed."}, {'sentence_id': 76, 'begin_time': 182920, 'end_time': 184900, 'text': "Yeah, she wouldn't even come out of her room."}, {'sentence_id': 77, 'begin_time': 186060, 'end_time': 187720, 'text': 'Did you really have to call her that?'}, {'sentence_id': 78, 'begin_time': 188260, 'end_time': 189200, 'text': 'A gold digger.'}, {'sentence_id': 79, 'begin_time': 189620, 'end_time': 190280, 'text': 'Well, you know what, dad?'}, {'sentence_id': 80, 'begin_time': 190460, 'end_time': 191240, 'text': 'It was a year ago.'}, {'sentence_id': 81, 'begin_time': 191540, 'end_time': 194160, 'text': 'And it was a natural question to ask.'}, {'sentence_id': 82, 'begin_time': 194360, 'end_time': 196480, 'text': "She's a beautiful, hot woman,"}, {'sentence_id': 83, 'begin_time': 196560, 'end_time': 198720, 'text': "and you're not exactly, you know."}, {'sentence_id': 84, 'begin_time': 200260, 'end_time': 201220, 'text': 'Not exactly what?'}, {'sentence_id': 85, 'begin_time': 202620, 'end_time': 204680, 'text': 'Um, Mitchell, little help.'}, {'sentence_id': 86, 'begin_time': 204680, 'end_time': 206380, 'text': 'No, you are doing great.'}, {'sentence_id': 87, 'begin_time': 206880, 'end_time': 209420, 'text': 'Now see, this is exactly why we sweep things under the rug,'}, {'sentence_id': 88, 'begin_time': 209940, 'end_time': 211240, 'text': "so people don't get hurt."}, {'sentence_id': 89, 'begin_time': 211440, 'end_time': 213660, 'text': 'Well, yeah, until you sweep too much under the rug.'}, {'sentence_id': 90, 'begin_time': 213780, 'end_time': 214820, 'text': 'Then you got a lumpy rug.'}, {'sentence_id': 91, 'begin_time': 215140, 'end_time': 217020, 'text': 'Creates a tripping hazard.'}, {'sentence_id': 92, 'begin_time': 217480, 'end_time': 218800, 'text': 'Open yourself up to lawsuits.'}, {'sentence_id': 93, 'begin_time': 219020, 'end_time': 220980, 'text': 'Boy, you can go a really long time without blinking.'}, {'sentence_id': 94, 'begin_time': 228300, 'end_time': 229840, 'text': "Gloria, it's Phil."}, {'sentence_id': 95, 'begin_time': 230980, 'end_time': 233560, 'text': 'Hi, can I talk to you for a second?'}, {'sentence_id': 96, 'begin_time': 234260, 'end_time': 238220, 'text': 'Claire likes to say you can be part of the problem or part of the solution.'}, {'sentence_id': 97, 'begin_time': 238965, 'end_time': 241805, 'text': 'Well, I happen to believe that you can be both.'}, {'sentence_id': 98, 'begin_time': 242985, 'end_time': 245465, 'text': 'Listen, Claire feels terrible.'}, {'sentence_id': 99, 'begin_time': 246725, 'end_time': 247885, 'text': "Why don't you talk to her?"}, {'sentence_id': 100, 'begin_time': 248805, 'end_time': 250905, 'text': 'Why, I know what she thinks.'}, {'sentence_id': 101, 'begin_time': 251485, 'end_time': 252245, 'text': 'A cold, dear.'}, {'sentence_id': 102, 'begin_time': 252665, 'end_time': 253805, 'text': "You know, she's saying gold."}, {'sentence_id': 103, 'begin_time': 253885, 'end_time': 254865, 'text': 'Yes, Phil.'}, {'sentence_id': 104, 'begin_time': 254945, 'end_time': 258425, 'text': 'Well, I know she said that, but that was a long time ago.'}, {'sentence_id': 105, 'begin_time': 258765, 'end_time': 259265, 'text': 'Before...'}, {'sentence_id': 106, 'begin_time': 259265, 'end_time': 261805, 'text': 'Do you buy me nice things?'}, {'sentence_id': 107, 'begin_time': 261805, 'end_time': 264125, 'text': 'Yes, of course, all beautiful things.'}, {'sentence_id': 108, 'begin_time': 264385, 'end_time': 268525, 'text': 'Look at this, yellow, red, blue, all the colors.'}, {'sentence_id': 109, 'begin_time': 268965, 'end_time': 270705, 'text': "Do you think I can't live without this?"}, {'sentence_id': 110, 'begin_time': 271265, 'end_time': 272645, 'text': 'Take them away, Phil.'}, {'sentence_id': 111, 'begin_time': 274765, 'end_time': 277685, 'text': "Gloria, we all know you'd be fine without underwear."}, {'sentence_id': 112, 'begin_time': 278305, 'end_time': 280425, 'text': "I mean, we know it's not about that."}, {'sentence_id': 113, 'begin_time': 280765, 'end_time': 284645, 'text': "No, it's about me not being accepted by my new family."}, {'sentence_id': 114, 'begin_time': 284905, 'end_time': 286125, 'text': 'That is not true.'}, {'sentence_id': 115, 'begin_time': 286745, 'end_time': 288785, 'text': "Gloria, look, you're a beautiful woman."}, {'sentence_id': 116, 'begin_time': 289205, 'end_time': 292205, 'text': "In fact, you're probably one of those beautiful women who doesn't even know it."}, {'sentence_id': 117, 'begin_time': 292365, 'end_time': 293205, 'text': 'No, I know it.'}, {'sentence_id': 118, 'begin_time': 294525, 'end_time': 298125, 'text': "So, it's natural for Claire to wonder about you and her dad."}, {'sentence_id': 119, 'begin_time': 299225, 'end_time': 301625, 'text': 'This family is very protective of each other.'}, {'sentence_id': 120, 'begin_time': 301765, 'end_time': 303745, 'text': 'I remember the first time Claire brought me home.'}, {'sentence_id': 121, 'begin_time': 304865, 'end_time': 307165, 'text': 'Do you think Jay thought I was good enough for his little girl?'}, {'sentence_id': 122, 'begin_time': 307565, 'end_time': 308365, 'text': 'No way.'}, {'sentence_id': 123, 'begin_time': 309585, 'end_time': 313125, 'text': 'But over time, he realized that I loved Claire as much as he did.'}, {'sentence_id': 124, 'begin_time': 314545, 'end_time': 316865, 'text': 'And by then, Mitch had brought Cam home, so I was golden.'}, {'sentence_id': 125, 'begin_time': 318225, 'end_time': 319905, 'text': 'Claire just needs a little time.'}, {'sentence_id': 126, 'begin_time': 321485, 'end_time': 324385, 'text': "Then trust me, she'll be the most loyal friend you've ever had."}]}]}}}
